      "mechanism_detail": "phase=Mint; (a) derive the slug from --path (or repo basename); (b) compute the consumer tenant ULID via derive-consumer-tenant Tool; (c) refuse-if-exists check at target_path (MUC-003 + MUC-007); (d) write to <target>.tmp then atomic os.replace to <target> (MUC-002 cancellation safety); (e) any signal mid-write leaves only the .tmp file — the next discovery run sweeps stale .tmp files at startup.",
