      ],
      "agent_instructions": "Derive the slug per the canonical derivation function (basename of --path or repo root, lowercased + sanitised). Invoke derive-consumer-tenant Tool to compute belongs_to_tenant. Check target_path.exists() — refuse with MUC-003 unless --update. Check sibling collision per MUC-007. Compose the Project entity JSON-LD. Write to <target>.tmp. os.replace to <target>. The .tmp + atomic-replace pair is non-negotiable for cancellation safety.",
